

Welcome to Salesforce Integration with TI system

Salesforce Integration with Trading System designed for maintaining consistency in the application data between multiple systems that need to be in sync. Which also helps to automate business processes and extend powerful APIs for communication between the systems.

It provides a single window where the users can manage notification and approval process of business transactions in a effective manner. One way we can achieve this by real-time synchronization of data between the systems is by using SOAP APIs, among other available options.
